{
  "texts": [
    "After the training, the participants could ask the experimenter any questions they might have.",
    "After making their choices for all twenty stimuli, participants were asked in an open-ended question to explain the criteria they used to decide whether each text was written by a human or an AI.",
    "They were then thanked for completing the second phase and invited to complete the third phase.",
    "In the third and final phase of the experiment, demographic data, such as gender, age, and field of study, were collected.",
    "The participants were then debriefed."
  ]
}